<h2 class="contentheading">
		<a href="/reviews/ohcd/98-epicas-extreme-universe-makeoverwith-an-orchestra.html" class="contentpagetitle">
		Epica’s Extreme Universe Makeover…with an Orchestra!	</a>
	</h2>


<div class="newsitem_tools">
<div class="newsitem_info">

			<span class="createdate"><!-- date and by -->
