<div class="newsitem_text">
<div class="news_item_article">
<p><img hspace="5" height="600" width="600" vspace="5" border="0" src="/images/stories/reviews/cd_reviews/epica/epica_cover.jpg" alt="" />Mark Jansen and his progressive symphony-metal band, Epica, started to hit the Gate Studio in Wolfsburg, Germany since March 2009 with producer Sascha Patch to begin work on their fourth studio album following the release of their first live CD <em>The Classical Conspiracy. </em>Released on October 16, 2009, <em>Design Your Universe </em>is yet another collection of majestically crafted songs that showcase the vast growth and development the band has gone through since their first album, <em>The Phantom Agony</em>.</p>

<div style="border: 1px solid rgb(102, 102, 102); margin: 10px; padding: 5px; float: right; width: 200px;">
